room_title: Escape room "The Box" by Escape Port Charlotte in Fort Myers
room_address: 3191 Harbor Blvd Unit C Port Charlotte, FL 33952
room_description:
Word is old man Whittington passed away. He was always the talk of the town. From how he stayed so young to the beautiful places he has traveled, but one thing that has the whole town stumped is a strange box. He traveled all over the world but no matter where he went, a strange box was always by his side. He never spoke of the box and some even say they think he is hiding something.
You find old man Whittington's front door unlocked and decide to find out once and for all what was in the box. You have 60 minutes. Do you think you can outsmart old man Whittington?
